comments: The learning phase was too fast paced for me. I would like to repeat in my mind the word a few times so i could remember it. I am pretty sure there was some pattern with colors of the figures, but i did not figure it out fast enough. I learned more with listening than writing - and the different colors sounded very close to each other. Overall seemed very hard for me to learn enough for the practical test. I didn't write any notes. The sound testing was really throwing me out of the zone. At the beginning i concentrated only at the figures shape, the different colors were really hard to distinguish.
